{
  "stem": "449.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Did you meet your wife in Modling?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I met my wife--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Ah, from-- from [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 1913 till 1928, only 15 years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Is that 15?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, yeah, in Modling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My wife I met after I came back from Egypt.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went to Egypt.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had-- I had to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I was drafted [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for the Austrian army in 19-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [INAUDIBLE]. 1917.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was drafted in 1917, prepared to start my military service in-- February, 1918.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was really 17 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I am born on December 13, 1900.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the law said, all people born in 1900 have to serve.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I was-- I was one of the last men in the-- in 1900, but one of the first men of the 20th century.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I had to serve in the Austrian army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what did you do in the army?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I remember, I was in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, I had-- because I had gymnasium, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I had the privilege after the gymnasium, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the-- the education permitted me to go in the officers' school for the infantry.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I had to, still, to go to that what they, the-- the non-officer [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] soldiers has to do.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to-- for instance, I had to stay guard on the poppy-- on the poppy field.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I know there was a huge-- that was in the Ukraine-- a huge poppy field.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had to guard there and watch that-- that nobody takes the poppies off.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can only imagine that maybe the military needed the poppy for medical purposes.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
